question:
What is the output of the following code?

```javascript
for (let i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {
  if (i === 3) {
    continue;
  }
  console.log(i);
}
```

What is the output of the following code?

```javascript
let sum = 0;
for (let i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {
  sum += i;
}
console.log(sum);
```

What is the output of the following code?

```javascript
let i = 0;
do {
  console.log(i);
  i++;
} while (i < 3);
```
